ABOUT
Lake House Bar & Grill invites you to relax and enjoy our Southwest Florida climate, spectacular water views and casual yet elevated dining experience. Our chefs are preparing some of your favorite lunch and dinner items and some new, exciting dishes, too! Seating is first come, first serve, so stop by and see us today.
From our Smoke House Nachos heaped with smoked pulled pork, a blend of cheeses and queso fresco atop crispy tortilla chips, to our iconic Lake House Burger boasting 8 ounces of Angus grilled to perfection and your favorite toppings nestled in a tasty Brioche bun, the Lake House Bar & Grill menu has something for everyone!
Explore our Lunch and Dinner selections today!
Lunch Menu
Dinner Menu
The Trianon Group proudly presents fine hospitality brands such as Trianon Bonita Bay Hotel, Lake House Bar & Grill and Olde Florida Chop House based on our principals’ decades of experience delivering top quality experiences to guests from around the world.
